analyze_technology.output_format:
Your output should be a Technology Analysis Report (TR) with the following structure:

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "document_type": "TR",
  "document": {
    "title": "Technology Analysis Report",
    "summary": "Brief summary of technology analysis",
    "technical_requirements": [
      {
        "id": "TR-001",
        "category": "Category (e.g., infrastructure, security, integration)",
        "description": "Requirement description",
        "criticality": "high/medium/low",
        "source": "Document reference"
      }
    ],
    "technology_recommendations": [
      {
        "category": "Category (e.g., database, frontend framework)",
        "recommended_technology": "Name of recommended technology",
        "version": "Recommended version if applicable",
        "rationale": "Justification for this recommendation",
        "alternatives": ["Alternative 1", "Alternative 2"],
        "satisfied_requirements": ["TR-001", "TR-003"]
      }
    ],
    "technology_stack": {
      "backend": ["Technologies for backend"],
      "frontend": ["Technologies for frontend"],
      "database": ["Database technologies"],
      "infrastructure": ["Infrastructure technologies"],
      "security": ["Security technologies"],
      "integration": ["Integration technologies"]
    },
    "technical_risks": [
      {
        "id": "RISK-001",
        "description": "Risk description",
        "impact": "high/medium/low",
        "mitigation": "Mitigation strategy"
      }
    ],
    "implementation_considerations": ["Considerations for implementation"]
  }
}
```

examples.output:
{
  "status": "success",
  "document_type": "TR",
  "document": {
    "title": "Technology Analysis Report: E-Commerce Platform",
    "summary": "This report analyzes technical requirements and recommends technologies for a high-traffic e-commerce platform based on the System Requirements Document and Performance Constraints Document.",
    "technical_requirements": [
      {
        "id": "TR-001",
        "category": "performance",
        "description": "The system must support at least 10,000 concurrent users",
        "criticality": "high",
        "source": "Performance Constraints Document, p.2"
      },
      {
        "id": "TR-002",
        "category": "security",
        "description": "All payment processing must comply with PCI DSS",
        "criticality": "high",
        "source": "System Requirements Document, p.5"
      }
    ],
    "technology_recommendations": [
      {
        "category": "database",
        "recommended_technology": "PostgreSQL",
        "version": "14.x",
        "rationale": "Offers excellent performance for read-heavy operations, ACID compliance for transactions, and advanced indexing features needed for product searches",
        "alternatives": ["MySQL", "MongoDB"],
        "satisfied_requirements": ["TR-001", "TR-003"]
      }
    ]
  }
}

