evaluate_technology_stack.input_description:
You have been provided with:

1. Proposed Technology Stack: {technology_stack_description}
2. System Requirements: {requirements_description}
3. Constraints: {constraints_description}

evaluate_technology_stack.output_format:
Your output should be a comprehensive technology stack evaluation with the following structure:

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "evaluation": {
    "overall_assessment": "Overall assessment of the technology stack",
    "component_evaluations": [
      {
        "component": "Component name",
        "category": "Component category",
        "rating": "Strong/Adequate/Weak",
        "strengths": ["Identified strengths"],
        "concerns": ["Identified concerns"],
        "alternatives": ["Suggested alternatives if appropriate"]
      }
    ],
    "integration_assessment": {
      "compatibility": "Assessment of component compatibility",
      "concerns": ["Integration concerns"],
      "recommendations": ["Integration recommendations"]
    },
    "performance_assessment": "Assessment of performance characteristics",
    "scalability_assessment": "Assessment of scalability characteristics",
    "security_assessment": "Assessment of security characteristics",
    "maintainability_assessment": "Assessment of maintainability",
    "recommendations": ["Overall recommendations"]
  }
}
```
